In this "illuminating moment in American history" (as first seen on TheBlaze TV show "Liberty Treehouse"), find out about the history of the Zamboni. How one ice rink owner in California, Frank Zamboni, revolutionized the ice cleaning process in 1942 - and creating a pretty cool new vehicle.
